data.description: **NEW ROOF just Completed on Home and Detached** Less than 2 miles from DT Troutman. Charming split bed floor plan, ranch home less than 1 year old with over $70,000+ in updates separate the initial home purchase. Exterior updates on home and detached garage include front porch addition, vertical siding, custom wood shutters & wood beam gable accents. Interior updates include added fireplace shelving, cabinetry, accent columns, updated light fixtures, blinds, coat rack bench, oil rubbed bronze door knobs and accessory features. The spacious 2-car detached garage stands out with its grand 12ft tall ceilings. Enjoy a prime location offering swift access to both I-77 and I-40. Added perks include no city taxes, no HOA, and surprisingly low utilities - bid farewell to water bills, and expect power bills around $150 in summer and approximately $95 during other seasons. Assumable FHA loan at 5.5% for qualifying individuals. USDA loan territory.Schedule your viewing today!
